com.cisco.pxgrid.stub.eps

Interface EPSQuery

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EPSQueryImpl

    public interface EPSQuery
    An interface with methods related to invoking actions in the Endpoint Protection Service (EPS). Clients typically receive an instance by invoking a static method such as com.cisco.xgrid.eps.client.EPSClientStub#createEPSQuery(com.cisco.xgrid.gcl.GridConnection).
